Class SpaceNode

  • java.lang.Object
    • main.java.SpaceNode

  • public class SpaceNode
extends java.lang.Object
    Container for the Space objects on the logical board. Object has the ability to know who its neighbors are.

    Matthew Coupal

      • equals

        public boolean equals(SpaceNode comparison)

        Parameters:
